Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.18,0:00:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Karl.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.58,0:00:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Lotte.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.95,0:00:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.65,0:00:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not really. What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.49,0:00:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,N-Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.65,0:00:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I was thinking we could get\Ntea or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.76,0:00:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought that we could\Ntalk a bit more
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.63,0:00:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,about the events\Nsurrounding Mr. Schuwald.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.53,0:00:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay, everything's fine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.90,0:00:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.03,0:00:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. I'm in a hurry right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.17,0:00:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,My father has a meeting\Nhe has to attend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.07,0:00:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.38,0:00:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,There's going to be a dance.\NI thought that we could...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.62,0:02:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The library will be closing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.03,0:02:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.93,0:02:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We're closing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.43,0:02:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That girl's here again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.14,0:03:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's beautiful...\NGod sure is unfair.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.04,0:03:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sure that she doesn't\Nhave any problems.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.05,0:03:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But that girl...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.88,0:03:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's closing time!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.62,0:03:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.12,0:03:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.50,0:03:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I've seen her somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.87,0:03:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,A dance?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.31,0:03:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.98,0:03:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not really interested in\Nthose kinds of things,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.85,0:03:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,but a friend forced me to\Nbuy some tickets.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.72,0:03:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. I can't tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.19,0:03:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.45,0:03:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a dinner with members\Nof the state assembly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.49,0:03:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a normal dinner party.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.83,0:03:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure there are lots of guys\Nwho'd escort you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.23,0:03:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.27,0:03:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.20,0:04:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not as if I really want to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.83,0:04:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.47,0:04:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.80,0:04:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You're investigating\NMargot Langer, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.54,0:04:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no need to erase it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.51,0:04:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm also investigating her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.28,0:04:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.11,0:04:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's for a paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.91,0:04:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Lotte Frank,\Na cultural anthropology major.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.02,0:04:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.59,0:04:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I see you're quite brilliant,\NMiss Nina Fortner.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.06,0:04:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the accountant murder case.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.33,0:05:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a newspaper article about\Nthe voice of god murder case.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.60,0:05:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is the middle-aged couple\Nmurder case.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.13,0:05:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You're amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.04,0:05:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I have confidence in my ability\Nto gather information,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.14,0:05:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,but you put me to shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.51,0:05:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been investigating\Nthe unsolved murder cases
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.84,0:05:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,that have happened in Bavaria\Nover the past four years.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.51,0:05:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you tell me more about the murder\Nof Margot Langer, the ex-prostitute?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.98,0:05:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I just told you what I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.62,0:05:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The child born to Margot Langer\Nand Hans Schuwald, the tycoon,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.59,0:05:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,has been recognized by his father\Nand is now his heir.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.60,0:05:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the possibility\Nthat his son was involved
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.13,0:05:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,in the events\Nsurrounding Schuwald?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.44,0:05:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not possible.\NNot at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.94,0:05:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.47,0:05:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You're rather enthusiastic\Nabout your topic.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.94,0:05:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,For someone who's just writing a paper,\Nyou seem pretty involved in your topic.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.48,0:05:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.38,0:05:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't for a research paper, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.42,0:06:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,To be honest,\NI'm looking for someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.73,0:06:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I ask you one question?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.13,0:06:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Do people like you have things\Nthey worry about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.03,0:06:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.23,0:06:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, beautiful girls like you get\Neverything they want, don't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.74,0:06:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you trying to say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.27,0:06:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,For example, you've never had\Nromantic problems, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.55,0:06:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay. You don't have\Nthe worries I have, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.52,0:06:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,God really is unfair.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.70,0:06:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Say! Want to come with me tonight\Nto a dance party?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.88,0:06:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really care for places like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.55,0:07:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, don't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.95,0:07:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys will talk to us as long\Nas you're with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.92,0:07:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Look. Everyone's looking at us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.82,0:07:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.99,0:07:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll just take the leftovers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.03,0:07:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Lotte...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.80,0:07:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.93,0:07:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, they're coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.70,0:07:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.43,0:07:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Constantine from\Nthe Supernatural Phenomenon Club!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.30,0:07:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Pleased to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.37,0:07:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,My goodness.\NA really weird one's come.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.04,0:07:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure got some nerve,\Ntalking to Nina with a face like yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.98,0:07:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, Lotte!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.78,0:07:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.02,0:07:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like to be\Nmy partner for tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.52,0:07:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.49,0:07:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.09,0:07:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you glad, Lotte?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.96,0:07:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be off now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.79,0:07:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait, Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.03,0:07:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not my type!\NHe's not my type at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.93,0:07:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay with me, Nina.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.43,0:07:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.54,0:08:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We're kind of depressing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.41,0:08:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.51,0:08:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah"? So many people\Ntalked to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.02,0:08:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina, you're too cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.32,0:08:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not trying to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.26,0:08:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm having fun for the\Nfirst time in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.49,0:08:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.33,0:08:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Students are hanging out and everyone is\Nhaving fun joking with each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.77,0:08:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.63,0:08:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina, are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.54,0:08:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,N-Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.14,0:08:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You're pretty straight-laced,\Ndespite your looks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.05,0:08:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's that supposed to mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.62,0:08:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Lotte.\NPlease, dance with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.10,0:08:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Woah, he's come again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.90,0:08:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You're being pushy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.50,0:09:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a little is fine. Just a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.54,0:09:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.81,0:09:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.51,0:09:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Let go of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.34,0:09:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.38,0:09:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not as if I'm asking you\Nbecause I like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.62,0:09:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?! That's rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.62,0:09:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, dance with me just once.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.26,0:09:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.89,0:09:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get paid if you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.53,0:09:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Paid?! What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.73,0:09:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't mean anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.03,0:09:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Karl asked me to.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.37,0:09:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,He asked me to be\Nyour partner for tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.07,0:09:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,By Karl?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.21,0:09:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So all you have to do is dance\Nwith me a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.15,0:09:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.05,0:09:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.35,0:09:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.52,0:09:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Just for one song is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.89,0:09:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.73,0:10:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow ow ow! Ow! Ow!\NSorry. It hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.77,0:10:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't do it anymore!\NI won't do it anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.00,0:10:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.44,0:10:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.29,0:10:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I liked him, that's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.03,0:10:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I liked Karl, that's why\NI helped him find his father.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.10,0:10:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I liked him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.70,0:10:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But ever since he proved\Nthat he's Schuwald's real son...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.74,0:10:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,He has business with his father.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.08,0:10:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,He promised his father something.\NHis father. His father.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.39,0:11:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It hurts. It hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.83,0:11:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I never thought that being dumped\Nwould hurt so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.03,0:11:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It does hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.23,0:11:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,There are only painful things.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.48,0:11:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's all right.\NIt'll be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.35,0:11:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Bad things don't last forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.55,0:11:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You mustn't let them continue,\Nall right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.20,0:11:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, I'll be going now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.37,0:11:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me where to contact you, Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.71,0:11:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. I still haven't found\Na place to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.81,0:11:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Then call my house!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.91,0:11:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Promise me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.08,0:11:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.98,0:12:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Today was fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.28,0:12:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you find the person\Nyou're looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.23,0:12:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina... She...\NI thought I saw her somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.41,0:12:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,She looks exactly like Johan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.37,0:12:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You're pretty good with that, Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.11,0:13:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's rather the efficiency of\Nthe gun rather than your skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.95,0:13:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That rifle was rejected as the official\Nsniper rifle of the German army,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.22,0:13:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,but it can hit the center of\Na 5-cm target from 300 meters away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.39,0:13:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Even an amateur could do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.73,0:13:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what\Nyou're going to shoot,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.13,0:13:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,but your aim gets better\Nthe closer you get to the target.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.70,0:13:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,All that's left is finding a place where\Nyou can get a clear shot at your target.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.51,0:13:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The bullets are .338 Lapua Magnums.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.38,0:13:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,There are four of them in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.21,0:13:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,But you don't have the time\Nto fire all four of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.35,0:13:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over if you don't finish\Nthe job on your first shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.81,0:14:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You come here every day, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.25,0:14:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Bird-watching?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.75,0:14:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.62,0:14:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,A lot of visitors come to\Nthis forest on Thursdays.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.92,0:15:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Those two young people with\Nthat old man and you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.20,0:15:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you like this forest?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.17,0:15:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.40,0:15:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Umm... What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.57,0:15:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.74,0:15:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm apologizing to this forest
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.88,0:15:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,and I have been for over 60 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.91,0:15:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Haven't seen him before.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.58,0:15:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,He's barely touched\Nmy special dishes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.25,0:16:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come on' answer today's quiz\Nto win fabulous prizes!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.62,0:16:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Our first contestant is\NMr. Weindler from Frankfurt!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.83,0:16:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Here's the prize' an RV!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.10,0:16:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Woah... It's what my family\Nhas always wanted.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.27,0:16:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mr. Weindler is very pleased!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.67,0:16:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It would be wonderful\Nto go camping in this!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.54,0:16:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But you'll only get it if you answer\Nten questions correctly.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.71,0:16:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The first question!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.33,0:17:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you planning to leave without\Ntouching anything again?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.50,0:17:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You came about a week ago,\Ndidn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.30,0:17:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I always remember my customers,\Nno matter how crowded it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.60,0:17:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're not hungry,\Nat least have this soup before you leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.87,0:17:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's on the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.31,0:17:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You look terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.14,0:17:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.41,0:18:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.28,0:18:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I can only shoot him in this forest!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.21,0:19:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.54,0:19:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I never thought that I'd trip after walking\Nin this forest after all these years.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.88,0:19:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I must be getting old.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.72,0:19:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think you have a fracture.\NI've applied first aid.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.92,0:19:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Afterwards, go to a hospital\Nand have someone take a look at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.09,0:19:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you a doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.80,0:19:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,When I first saw you,\NI thought you were a hunter.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.93,0:19:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,But that doesn't seem to be the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.18,0:19:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm amazed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.44,0:19:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.88,0:19:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The birds.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.11,0:19:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,They're gathering.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.25,0:19:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Long ago, there was a man on whose\Nshoulder wild birds would come to rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.12,0:20:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The wild birds would come and rest\Non his hand when he held it out like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.10,0:20:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,When he was a child, he would always\Nspend his time in the forest with the birds.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.97,0:20:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,But then, the age of Hitler came.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.91,0:20:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The man became a member\Nof the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.78,0:20:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The Nationalist Socialist German\NWorkers Party truly believed
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.81,0:20:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,they could turn this country\Ninto an ideal one.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.95,0:20:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The man received an order.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.42,0:20:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,A vicious criminal escaped into this forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.23,0:20:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,He was chosen to go after him\Nsince he was familiar with the forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.13,0:20:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,"Shoot that vicious criminal\Nwhen you find him"' they said.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.84,0:20:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The man chased the vicious criminal\Nthrough the forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.24,0:20:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,He chased him and chased him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.81,0:20:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,But when he finally cornered him,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.95,0:20:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,the vicious criminal was just an\Nordinary foreigner you'd see anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.89,0:21:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But it didn't matter who\Nthe foreigner was.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.66,0:21:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The man had no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.09,0:21:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,He carried out his orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.55,0:21:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Since then, the birds never came\Nto rest on his shoulder.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.45,0:21:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,60 years later, he's still apologizing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.49,0:21:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I'm sorry"' he tells them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.03,0:21:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But the birds never come near him.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.08,0:22:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.86,0:22:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right.\NNever again...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.73,0:22:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Never again will blood be spilled\Nin this forest again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.83,0:22:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right?
